id she suffered a torrent of online threats in the wake of a contentious scene at the Games' opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a torrent\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"online threats\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"the wake\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"a contentious scene\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' opening ceremony\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lawyer for Butch told The Associated Press that she had filed a formal legal complaint alleging online harassment, death threats, and insults.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.919087716357601e-12, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lawyer\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"a formal legal complaint\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"online harassment\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"death threats\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"insults\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The lawyer, Audrey Msellati, said the complaint does not name any specific perpetrator or perpetrators of the alleged crimes.\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 658, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\", \"s