 Supper,\\\"critics interpreted part of the showthat featured Butch as a mockery of Leonardo Da Vinci's painting showing Jesus Christ and his apostles.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9999902065849054, \"rank\": 9.793491445819553e-06, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 1295, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1979367439474973e-17, \"text\": \"Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.1768356205228e-35, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999898200258, \"rank\": 1.018016009539746e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony'sartistic director\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper,\\\"critics\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"the showthat featured Butch\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"a mockery\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"his apostles\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch, who calls herself a \\\"love activist,\\\" wore a silver headdress that looked like a halo as she got a party going during her segment of the show.\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"love activist\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver headdress\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"a halo\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"a party\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"her segment\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Drag artists, dancers and others flanked Butch on both sides.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Drag artists\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trump, in the United States, said Monday he thought it was \\\"a disgrace.\\\"\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999993879101, \"rank\": 6.12069727298882e-10, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.7186861219027149, \"rank\": 0.3914280094244647, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very open-minded,\\\" the former president and current Republican nominee told Fox News host Laura Ingraham, who specifically asked about comparisons to \\\"The Last Supper,\\\" \\\"but I thought what they did was a disgrace.\\\"\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9999997653208359, \"rank\": 2.325110263413827e-07, \"text\": \"Republican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.534278510034267e-26, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}, {\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.768182378994437e-30, \"text\": \"Laura Ingraham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Ingraham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the former president\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"comparisons\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French Catholic bishops and others were among those who said Christians had been hurt and offended.Paris Olympics organizers have saidthere was \\\"never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group\\\" and that the intent was to \\\"celebrate community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9982522831061394, \"rank\": 0.001729012975498579, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1878, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999998317330352, \"rank\": 1.1302927743873547e-07, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8162775601525999, \"rank\": 0.22453382302765296, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris Olympics organizers\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"the intent\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly has said he saw the moment as a celebration of diversity, and the table on which Butch spun her tunes as a tribute to feasting and French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2276, \"end\": 2282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9982522831061394, \"rank\": 0.001729012975498579, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"a celebration\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"her tunes\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"a tribute\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock,\\\" Jolly said.\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wish\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Performer Philippe Katerine,who appeared in the next scenepainted blue and nearly nude in a tribute to Dionysus, also told Le Monde newspaper that \\\"The Last Supper\\\" had not been referenced at all in preparations for the overall sketch.\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippe Katerine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\"}, {\"begin\": 2572, \"end\": 2580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.810991447721583e-23, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 2592, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Monde\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Monde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tribute\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"preparations\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall sketch\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement of her own, posted on Instagram, Butch said: \\\"Whatever some may say, I exist.\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2743, \"end\": 2752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4472554330640431e-39, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2709, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"Whatever\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never been ashamed of who I am, and I take responsibility for everything - including my artistic choices.\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"my artistic choices\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All my life, I have refused to be a victim: I will not shut up.\\\"\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a victim\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said she \\\"was extremely honored\\\" to perform in Friday's ceremony and \\\"my heart is still full of joy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 3083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Friday's ceremony\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am committed, and I am proud.\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Proud of who I am, of what I am, and of what I embody, both for my loved ones and for millions of French people.\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3216, \"end\": 3229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my loved ones\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My France is France !\\\"\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3234, \"end\": 3240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996963947629663, \"rank\": 0.00016735618464298687, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3244, \"end\": 3250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996963947629663, \"rank\": 0.00016735618464298687, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she wrote.\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an AP interview Tuesday, Msellati described Butch as in \\\"a fighting spirit\\\" - eager to defend herself and her choices, and still very proud of her participation.\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.78777456866461e-22, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Msellati\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3302}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3318}, {\"ngram\": \"a fighting spirit\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3343}, {\"ngram\": \"her choices\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3386}, {\"ngram\": \"her participation\", \"from\": 3412, \"to\": 3429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has no regrets, even now,\\\" the lawyer said.\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no regrets\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"the lawyer\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said hateful messages targeting Butch are \\\"arriving almost every minute,\\\" and that Jolly and the ceremony's drag artists have also been targeted by cyberbullying.\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hateful messages\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3522}, {\"ngram\": \"Jolly\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3573}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony's drag artists\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another performer in the controversial scene, drag queen Paloma, said Tuesday that she had not filed her own complaint.\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3706, \"end\": 3712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.740292663149033e-12, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another performer\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3666}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversial scene\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3693}, {\"ngram\": \"her own complaint\", \"from\": 3750, \"to\": 3767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, she said, \\\"if the insults continue, I will join my friend Barbara Butch in her approach.\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3833, \"end\": 3846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the insults\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3800}, {\"ngram\": \"my friend\", \"from\": 3823, \"to\": 3832}, {\"ngram\": \"her approach\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, I am trying to focus on the on the thousands of loving messages I receive.\\\"\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the thousands\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 3917}, {\"ngram\": \"loving messages\", \"from\": 3921, \"to\": 3936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the criticism, Paloma said her \\\"first reaction is to say that if Donald Trump is not reacting, then we have not done our job.\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 4078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3968, \"end\": 3974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 5.740292663149033e-12, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 4018, \"end\": 4030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.775573461255671e-12, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the criticism\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"her \\\"first reaction\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 3999}, {\"ngram\": \"our job\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, we were going to get a negative reaction no matter what we did.\\\"\", \"from\": 4079, \"to\": 4158, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a negative reaction\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also said it was hypocritical for critics to use religion as a basis for \\\"a reaction that is very homophobic, very transphobic, queer-phobic, drag-phobic, even antisemitic and fatphobic.\\\"\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"critics\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4204}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4220}, {\"ngram\": \"a basis\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4231}, {\"ngram\": \"a reaction\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And another drag queen in the scene, Piche, said she was \\\"really happy that queer people were able to be represented in this show.\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another drag queen\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4374}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4387}, {\"ngram\": \"Piche\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4394}, {\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 4428, \"to\": 4440}, {\"ngram\": \"this show\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no moment that the idea of offending someone or a religion was on somebody's mind.\", \"from\": 4483, \"to\": 4575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no moment\", \"from\": 4493, \"to\": 4502}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"a religion\", \"from\": 4541, \"to\": 4551}, {\"ngram\": \"somebod